<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_448_r1l2">Wır ~ dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc Bekennen etc Vmb ſölıch <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd klag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l4">als <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> hanns <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Eglofſtein <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_448_r1l3">pfleger vnd </ab></add> <expan>lantrıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu Awrbach getan hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l5">vnd tut vor <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan> ʒu Awrbach auf <expan>Grefemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> mıt ſeınr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l6"><expan>ʒugehöru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd auf alles das . daʒ wır vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> lant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l7">gerıcht lıgend <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Daʒ wır <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıenern <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> heͣrlein vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l8">. <expan cert="unknown">C</expan> . Beheım <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd geben . wollen vnd <expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt vnd macht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l9"><expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> vnſre vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> güter von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l10">gen Jm <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> vnd ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tretten</expan> ʒu <expan>gewin<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ʒu verluſt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l11">ʒu allem <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıgelt</expan> etc Geben ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_448" id="223r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
